questlog (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix: the session list could hang after a few rows over a large recent
    history; a session file above 64 KB aborted the scan under Tcl 9's
    strict UTF-8 decoding.
  * Single-file executable: a zipfs mkimg build runs with no install on a
    host that has the Tcl 9 runtime.
  * Installation guide added (docs/installation.md).
  * Runs on macOS: process-liveness, launch directory, and reveal-in-folder
    no longer assume Linux.
  * Search runs on Enter instead of on every keystroke.
  * Right-click a search-result row to open its session menu.
  * Search hits marked by an amber background; the design's role palette,
    pill labels, and toolbar details adopted.

